The paper discusses the use of Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) and Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs) for image captioning, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) research. The paper also mentions the use of beam search algorithm, which is a common optimization technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed model using various metrics, which is a common practice in information retrieval (cs.IR) research.
